---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Safeguarding Children Policy | Wroughton & Wichelstowe FC"
  description="Safeguarding policy for Wroughton & Wichelstowe FC."
>
  <section class="bg-[#04163a] py-24 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">
      <a
        href="/policies"
        class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-300 hover:text-blue-200"
      >
        ← Back to policies
      </a>

      <div class="mt-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-10">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-light tracking-tight">
          Safeguarding Children Policy
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-300">
          Wroughton & Wichelstowe FC is committed to safeguarding and
          promoting the welfare of children and young people. The club
          expects all coaches, volunteers, parents, players and visitors
          to share this commitment.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-slate-300">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">
              Our Commitment
            </h2>

            <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
              We aim to provide a safe, inclusive and positive environment
              where children can enjoy football, develop confidence and
              participate free from abuse, bullying, discrimination or harm.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">
              Safeguarding Principles
            </h2>

            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-3 pl-6">
              <li>The welfare of the child is paramount.</li>
              <li>All children have the right to protection from harm.</li>
              <li>All safeguarding concerns will be taken seriously.</li>
              <li>All volunteers and coaches are expected to follow FA safeguarding guidance.</li>
              <li>The club will promote inclusion and respect at all times.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">
              Reporting Concerns
            </h2>

            <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
              Any safeguarding concern should be reported immediately to the
              club Welfare Officer or an appropriate safeguarding authority.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">
              Contact
            </h2>

            <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed">
              Club Welfare Officer details will be published here.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>